# Sūra XIV.: Ibrāhīm, or Abraham.

### Section 3

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/014/014_013.gif)

13. Waq<u>a</u>la alla<u>th</u>eena kafaroo lirusulihim lanukhrijannakum
min ar<u>d</u>in<u>a</u> aw lataAAoodunna fee millatin<u>a</u>
